Danny welcomes Queen/Icon/Legend Fran Drescher to Everything Iconic! They talk about health and wellness (visit cancerschmancer.org), The Nanny, The Beautician and the Beast, Indebted (season finale on Thursday on NBC), RHONY, and more!


YOUTUBE: https://www.youtube.com/dannypellegrino1

For tickets to the Chicago live show: https://bit.ly/3bc6QLX
